532
00:39:07,650 --> 00:39:09,749
That's a fresh take you can have because you're not Korean.

533
00:39:09,750 --> 00:39:11,850
A completely new interpretation of ssam.

534
00:39:12,650 --> 00:39:16,960
But in terms of storytelling, I feel like it's interesting.

535
00:39:17,020 --> 00:39:21,190
So I was thinking, maybe there is a chance to win.

536
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:27,530
All right, now for our last team. Team Luvita and Lee Sae On.

537
00:39:27,900 --> 00:39:31,669
Normally, when we just talk, she's so sweet.

538
00:39:31,670 --> 00:39:37,009
But when we're on a mission, she gets fierce.

539
00:39:37,010 --> 00:39:38,710
"Sweet and Fierce Ssam."

540
00:39:40,810 --> 00:39:43,280
It's like a ssam, but we used mugwort.

541
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:47,720
The texture of the pork belly, when it's on the grill,

542
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:51,260
it starts to crisp up, right? So I wanted to give that texture...

543
00:39:51,320 --> 00:39:52,590
to the pumpkin bread.

544
00:39:53,990 --> 00:39:55,689
On the surface, I use walnuts to recreate...

545
00:39:55,690 --> 00:39:57,260
the crispness of pork belly.

546
00:40:05,970 --> 00:40:09,240
Like the experience of making the ssam yourself.

547
00:40:10,010 --> 00:40:12,510
Out of all the ssam desserts today,

548
00:40:12,580 --> 00:40:17,220
I think you've captured the essence of ssam the best.

549
00:40:17,280 --> 00:40:22,290
However, I didn't feel the flavors really worked well together.

550
00:40:22,320 --> 00:40:25,460
The gochujang butter was too overpowering,

551
00:40:26,060 --> 00:40:28,790
while the mascarpone was too bland.

552
00:40:28,860 --> 00:40:32,030
So the flavor fell a little short of my expectations.

553
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:35,670
Well, I have a slightly different opinion on that.

554
00:40:35,730 --> 00:40:39,740
The gochujang was very overpowering when I tasted it on its own.

555
00:40:39,800 --> 00:40:44,080
But I tried it for the first time, I only used a tiny amount.

556
00:40:44,140 --> 00:40:47,550
And with that amount, I felt the balance was perfect.

557
00:40:47,610 --> 00:40:51,920
So for me, this was a refreshing and fun dessert.

558
00:40:51,980 --> 00:40:53,350
- Thank you. - Thank you.

559
00:40:54,050 --> 00:40:57,390
This is a flavor you'd expect to see.

560
00:40:57,460 --> 00:40:59,060
But as for what the public would think...

561
00:40:59,120 --> 00:41:02,830
In terms of genre, they're night and day.

562
00:41:02,890 --> 00:41:05,530
So, who gets first place?

563
00:41:05,600 --> 00:41:09,830
You worked so hard to create such incredible results in a short time.

564
00:41:09,900 --> 00:41:13,000
This was a really tough decision.

565
00:41:13,070 --> 00:41:15,470
- Oh, no. - Difficult.

566
00:41:15,540 --> 00:41:17,740
This is way too real.

567
00:41:23,250 --> 00:41:26,320
First, let's start with the dessert that fell a bit short today.

568
00:41:30,460 --> 00:41:31,920
Everyone was excellent,

569
00:41:33,330 --> 00:41:38,030
but Jan Nichcha and Seung Ha's team.

570
00:41:40,230 --> 00:41:44,670
When I actually ate it, the rice sheet was a bit gummy,

571
00:41:44,740 --> 00:41:46,240
and it got stuck between my teeth.

572
00:41:46,300 --> 00:41:50,280
I think if the wrap had been a little lighter for that one bite,

573
00:41:50,340 --> 00:41:52,080
it would've been better.

574
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:55,110
That's my fault.

575
00:41:56,920 --> 00:41:59,349
I was a little sad.

576
00:41:59,350 --> 00:42:02,589
I wasn't sad for myself,

577
00:42:02,590 --> 00:42:04,860
but for Seung Ha.

578
00:42:05,490 --> 00:42:08,189
Honestly, when we heard we came in last,

579
00:42:08,190 --> 00:42:12,160
Jan Nichcha was smiling, but she looked so sad...

580
00:42:12,460 --> 00:42:14,230
My heart went out to her.

581
00:42:14,530 --> 00:42:16,870
Jan Nichcha, I'll get you to Singapore.

582
00:42:18,340 --> 00:42:22,410
The second anticipated K-dessert to be featured on the menu is...

583
00:42:26,880 --> 00:42:27,980
It's...
